    "We validate multiple actions in multiple scenarios and report the user study result.",
    "The user study is to determine if the generated motions matched the command intents and fitted with the lane map.",
    "We see that our method demonstrated a significant advantage in generating motions from language commands.",
    "Additionally, it maintained a high rate of keeping the trajectories within the lane boundaries.",
    "Conclusions and LimitationsThis paper introduces ChatSim, the first system for editing 3D driving scene simulations via language commands and realistic rendering with import of external digital assets."
